				<td colspan="2"><span>Im hoping some of the other bards can answer some questions regarding the first fight in DN because Im attempting to get my guild make an attempt and hopefully if theres a good walkthru someone can point me too it.
<br />

<br />
Anyway, here are the questions I have regarding the adds:
<br />

<br />
1. Which ones are not mezzable?
<br />
2. Which ones are not slowable? 
<br />
3. Which mobs double and which quad hit?
<br />

<br />
Thats about all I dont know about them but theres also the issue of the Draconic abomination Ive heard about for this so I have some questions regarding him as well.
<br />

<br />
1. What % does he spawn at? or is it at Vesthrons death?
<br />
2. Is he slowable?
<br />
3. How much does he hit for and does he quad or double?
<br />
4. Does he have an AoE? and if yes what are the details of that AoE
<br />

<br />
and my last question regarding this fight is whats the respawn? Ild like to do this back to back if possible and then start taking care of DN2 fight for my fellow guild bards.
<br />

<br />
Thanks for any info you guys can give me.
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
