				<td colspan="2"><span>If you have the raid positions as far away from the doorway as possible, the majority of the spawns are not an issue. The easiest way to handle the zombies is to simply off-tank them while the rest of the raid burns the dragon.  Then you can simply pick off the zombies one at a time.  You can try to kite them, but honestly i think it makes the encounter harder than it needs to be.</span></td>
