				<td colspan="2"><span>I did this fight last night with a total of 22 people - 3 tanks 3 clerics (but 2 were bots). We're not fully EP equipped, but have killed FR and tried out Coirnav and Xegony a few times. Pally and War got agro on the Zombies after my hand-in and kept them fully occupied for the duration.  MT got agro on Vesthon and the rest was history.  Biggest problem was that the Chetaris started respawning during the event. Obviously I'd taken too long to brief my guildmates on what was about to happen.
<br />

<br />
1. What % does he spawn at? or is it at Vesthrons death? 
<br />
At about 20% Vesthon goes poof and the Draconic Abomination will spawn on top of you
<br />

<br />
2. Is he slowable? 
<br />
YES
<br />

<br />
3. How much does he hit for and does he quad or double? 
<br />
He only hit me a few times before the tank got agro, and those hits were only for around 400. Not sure if he doubles/quads etc, but the tank said something along the lines of &quot;this guy is a wimp.&quot; Tank has about 12.5K hp, 2200AC and over 600AAs.
<br />

<br />
4. Does he have an AoE? and if yes what are the details of that AoE 
<br />
The Abomination has AE rampage, dont know if he has an AE at all (if he did, it didnt go off at all during my fight). Ramp was hitting me for about 300hp during the fight.
<br />
</span></td>
